Now, however, straw bags are making a real triumph and fashion fans have exchanged their fancy designer bags for simple straw bags for the summer months.
It’s not just a beach bag, but it’s equally popular today as a street bag, and the bravest women even walk into the office with it.
However, it is worth first learning whether the boss is still sitting on such a summer look or whether it is still worth pushing the notebook and notebook to a slightly more formal sumadan.
The variety has made straw bags a true summer’s love for women.
For example, when reading foreign fashion blogs, the first thing that stands out is that fashion gourmands are the first thing on a holiday trip to the local market and buy themselves a straw bag, which will be loyal to the whole holiday time, and which accompanies them on the beach, in the market, as well as hanging out with their girlfriends on the town.
